Setting up Active Directory on the server 
 Link that I followed: https://xpertstec.com/microsoft/microsoft-windows-server/how-to-install-active-directory-windows-server-core-2022/

following the link we know that we have a wierd name for our server so we will change that name of the computer by switching back to our Domain controller terminal and uisng sconfig and selecting the option of Computer Name
and changing it as Domain-Controller1 

